# Deployment (Template)

This repo intentionally does not track `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md` (local-only). Use this file as a starting point:

1) Copy `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md.example` to `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md` locally.
2) Add environment-specific notes (domains, dashboards, runbook links).
3) Keep `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md` untracked (it is gitignored).

## Backend (Railway)

- Dockerfile: `backend/Dockerfile`
- Healthcheck: `/api/v1/health`
- Set variables from `.env.example` before first deploy.

Verify:

```bash
curl -sS https://<railway-url>/api/v1/health
curl -sS https://<railway-url>/api/v1/stats
```

## Frontend (Vercel)

- Root directory: `frontend/`
- Env: `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://<railway-url>`

Verify:

- `/`
- `/projects`
- `/settlement`
